{"data":{"actions":[{"callId":"chatcmpl-tool-9e701763ad81ca37","input":{"filename":"brand_voice_reviewer_action_report.md","title":"Brand Voice Reviewer Prioritized Action Report","markdown":"# Brand Voice Reviewer Prioritized Action Report\n\n**Context**: Analysis of operational records yielded three key items (total risk 17, opportunity 10.1). Evidence sources: dossier load and `analyze_records` output.\n\n## 1. Urgent: \"Brand voice reviewer priority case\" (ID 18-A)\n- **Status**: urgent\n- **Impact**: 47,706 (high)\n- **Risk Score**: 9 (high)\n- **Opportunity Score**: 6.8\n- **Action**: Allocate immediate resources to resolve this case. The record describes the highest‑impact open item requiring linting of copy for tone, banned phrases, and evidence compliance. \n- **Next Steps**:\n  1. Assign senior reviewer.\n  2. Verify copy samples against brand guidelines.\n  3. Document any banned phrase violations and required revisions.\n  4. Close the record within 2 business days.\n\n## 2. Blocked: \"Brand voice reviewer blocked follow‑up\" (ID 18-C)\n- **Status**: blocked (requires cross‑functional coordination)\n- **Impact**: 21,798\n- **Risk Score**: 7\n- **Opportunity Score**: 2.2\n- **Action**: Initiate coordination with the Legal and Product teams to unblock. The block stems from pending policy clarification.\n- **Next Steps**:\n  1. Schedule a sync meeting (target: within 3 days).\n  2. Clarify policy on newly‑added terminology.\n  3. Update the brand‑voice checklist accordingly.\n  4. Once cleared, re‑prioritize this item as “high”.\n\n## 3. Routine: \"Brand voice reviewer routine queue item\" (ID 18-B)\n- **Status**: in_review\n- **Impact**: 11,034\n- **Risk Score**: 1 (low)\n- **Opportunity Score**: 1.1\n- **Action**: Continue standard review workflow. Use this item as a benchmark for process efficiency.\n- **Next Steps**:\n  1. Complete the review using the existing checklist.\n  2. Log any minor tone adjustments for future pattern analysis.\n  3. Close item once approved.\n\n## Prioritization Summary\n| Rank | Record ID | Impact | Risk | Action | Owner |\n|------|-----------|--------|------|--------|-------|\n| 1 | 18-A | 47,706 | 9 (high) | Immediate resolution | Marketing |\n| 2 | 18-C | 21,798 | 7 (medium) | Unblock via cross‑functional sync | Marketing |\n| 3 | 18-B | 11,034 | 1 (low) | Routine processing | Marketing |\n\n**Assumptions**:\n- Impact numbers directly reflect business value as defined by internal scoring.\n- Risk scores are on a 0‑10 scale; higher means greater urgency.\n- No additional hidden dependencies beyond those listed.\n\n**Next Actions**:\n1. Execute the outlined steps for each record.\n2. Update the operational dashboard with progress status.\n3. Re‑run `analyze_records` in one week to reassess risk/opportunity shifts.\n\n*Report generated based on loaded dossier and analyzed records.*"},"kind":"tool-call","toolName":"write_report"}],"sequence":0,"stepIndex":3,"turnId":"turn_0"},"type":"actions.requested","meta":{"at":"2026-06-18T15:13:07.621Z"}}
